<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6830] Update the Woodstox API</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6830</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Solr uses a really old version (3.2.7) of the Woddstox API, the current stable version being 4.4.1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This old version is packaged in the same jar with an equally old version of StAX2 API. This makes it difficult to update just the StAX API with a more recent version - in my application I ran into this when trying to use StAXON.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose to update to Woodstox 4.4.1 and StAX2 3.1.4.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
